name: land-use-data-for-south-louisiana-utm-15n-nad83-lra-2007-landuse-slouisiana
notes: This GIS shapefile data set illustrates land use data for the 35 parishes in the Louisiana Speaks Regional Plan South Louisiana study area. The data set includes residential, commercial, industrial, civic and institutional, and parks and open space data.
